@NODE "Best" "Part 58 - The DISKDOCTOR Command - The BEST Method"

@{B}@{U}The BEST Method@{UB}@{UU}

Without a doubt, the best method of recovery when you have a corrupt disk
is to get out your backup copy and make another copy of it, then reformat
the corrupt disk.

You DO keep backups of all your disks, don't you?!?!?!


